ike.com/originalPosts/67ef86d96403deeedb4989cf</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://m.okjike.com/originalPosts/67ef86d96403deeedb4989cf</guid><pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 07:14:33 GMT</pubDate><author>Zeeland_</author></item><item><title>最近用量实在太多，才一周就用完了这一个月的额度https://codeium.com/refer?referral_code=96aab323ed</title><description>最近用量实在太多，才一周就用完了这一个月的额度https://codeium.com/refer?referral_code=96aab323ed&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://cdnv2.ruguoapp.com/FhsW70AghhTq6cu9Qvhh3svcXBsgv3.png&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;</description><link>https://m.okjike.com/originalPosts/67eeaf48a5495cd94f58cf95</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://m.okjike.com/originalPosts/67eeaf48a5495cd94f58cf95</guid><pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 15:54:48 GMT</pubDate><author>不善奔跑的李二牛</author></item><item><title>好！开学！</title><description>好！开学！&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://cdnv2.ruguoapp.com/Fu_qOUoim65MT0GcYDZLt4JfWWepv3.png&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;</description><link>https://m.okjike.com/originalPosts/67ee356c9bda4a11572b3048</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://m.okjike.com/originalPosts/67ee356c9bda4a11572b3048</guid><pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 07:14:52 GMT</pubDate><author>一盘大萝北</author></item><item><title>是这样的，不建议养成这样随口应答的习惯，对于每一个问题，都请开动脑子想一想。</title><description>是这样的，不建议养成这样随口应答的习惯，对于每一个问题，都请开动脑子想一想。&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://cdnv2.ruguoapp.com/FnIoUJBaUTd69cmmhDuyNbDHQ6jlv3.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;</description><link>https://m.okjike.com/originalPosts/67edd072070109da49b60976</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://m.okjike.com/originalPosts/67edd072070109da49b60976</guid><pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 00:04:02 GMT</pubDate><author>哥飞</author></item><item><title>以前觉得他们10万美金很多，难以企及。 现在自己身边人单枪匹马也做到了之后，觉得原来好像也不难。 所以我才敢喊出“让更多月薪两三万人民币的优秀程序员实现年...</title><description>以前觉得他们10万美金很多，难以企及。&lt;br&gt;现在自己身边人单枪匹马也做到了之后，觉得原来好像也不难。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;所以我才敢喊出“让更多月薪两三万人民币的优秀程序员实现年收入二三十万美金”的口号。&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;ht